{
  "texts": [
    "The approach proposed will become more accurate as the amount of data used for fine-tuning increases.",
    "Fifth, it is clear that the potential of transformer models in detecting text written by AI is large.",
    "Nonetheless, the approach proposed is not definitive and certainly has margin for improvement.",
    "It is crucial to bear in mind the possibility for error in such tools, particularly dependent on the fine-tuning process.",
    "This limitation is visible in the experiment conducted where applying a model fine-tuned using GPT-3.5 text in texts generated by Bard, revealed lower performances."
  ]
}